OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump said in an
OL,8,Feight-minute video posted on his Truth
OL,9,FSocial that the U.S. has begun "major
OL,10,Fcombat operations in Iran." He claimed
OL,11,FIran has continued to develop its
OL,12,Fnuclear programme and plans to develop
OL,13,Fmissiles to reach U.S. and appealed to
OL,14,Fthe Iranian people to "take over your
OL,15,Fgovernment."
OL,17,FHere's Trump's address in full:
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@[O]vD@WOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
