OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FA short time ago, the United States
OL,8,Fmilitary began major combat operations
OL,9,Fin Iran. Our objective is to defend
OL,10,Fthe American people by eliminating
OL,11,Fimminent threats from the Iranian
OL,12,Fregime. A vicious group of very hard,
OL,13,Fterrible people. Its menacing
OL,14,Factivities directly endanger the
OL,15,FUnited States, our troops, our bases
OL,16,Foverseas, and our allies throughout
OL,17,Fthe world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
