OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FFor 47 years, the Iranian regime has
OL,8,Fchanted Death to America and waged an
OL,9,Funending campaign of bloodshed and
OL,10,Fmass murder, targeting the United
OL,11,FStates, our troops and the innocent
OL,12,Fpeople in many, many countries. Among
OL,13,Fthe regime's very first acts was to
OL,14,Fback a violent takeover of the U.S.
OL,15,FEmbassy in Tehran, holding dozens of
OL,16,FAmerican hostages for 444 days. In
OL,17,F1983, Iran's proxies carried out the
OL,18,Fmarine barracks bombing in Beirut that
OL,19,Fkilled 241 American military personnel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
