OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FIn 2000, they knew and were probably
OL,8,Finvolved with the attack on the USS
OL,9,FCole. Many died. Iranian forces killed
OL,10,Fand maimed hundreds of American
OL,11,Fservice members in Iraq. The regime's
OL,12,Fproxies have continued to launch
OL,13,Fcountless attacks against American
OL,14,Fforces stationed in the Middle East in
OL,15,Frecent years, as well as U.S. naval
OL,16,Fand commercial vessels and
OL,17,Finternational shipping lines. It's
OL,18,Fbeen mass terror, and we're not going
OL,19,Fto put up with it any longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
