OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FFrom Lebanon to Yemen and Syria to
OL,8,FIraq, the regime has armed, trained
OL,9,Fand funded terrorist militias that
OL,10,Fhave soaked the earth with blood and
OL,11,Fguts. And it was Iran's proxy, Hamas,
OL,12,Fthat launched the monstrous Oct. 7
OL,13,Fattacks on Israel, slaughtering more
OL,14,Fthan 1,000 innocent people, including
OL,15,F46 Americans, while taking 12 of our
OL,16,Fcitizens hostage. It was brutal,
OL,17,Fsomething like the world has never
OL,18,Fseen before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
