OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FIran is the world's number one state
OL,8,Fsponsor of terror, and just recently
OL,9,Fkilled tens of thousands of its own
OL,10,Fcitizens on the street as they
OL,11,Fprotested. It has always been the
OL,12,Fpolicy of the United States, in
OL,13,Fparticular my administration, that
OL,14,Fthis terrorist regime can never have a
OL,15,Fnuclear weapon. I'll say it again,
OL,16,Fthey can never have a nuclear weapon.
OL,17,FThat is why in Operation Midnight
OL,18,FHammer last June, we obliterated the
OL,19,Fregime's nuclear program at Fordo,
OL,20,FNatanz and Isfahan. After that attack,
OL,21,Fwe warned them never to resume their
OL,22,Fmalicious pursuit of nuclear weapons,
OL,23,Fand we sought repeatedly to make a
OL,24,Fdeal. We tried. They wanted to do it.
OL,25,FThey didn't want to do it. Again they
OL,26,Fwanted to do it. They didn't want to
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
