OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FThey've rejected every opportunity to
OL,8,Frenounce their nuclear ambitions, and
OL,9,Fwe can't take it anymore. Instead,
OL,10,Fthey attempted to rebuild their
OL,11,Fnuclear program and to continue
OL,12,Fdeveloping the long range missiles
OL,13,Fthat can now threaten our very good
OL,14,Ffriends and allies in Europe, our
OL,15,Ftroops stationed overseas, and could
OL,16,Fsoon reach the American homeland. Just
OL,17,Fimagine how emboldened this regime
OL,18,Fwould be if they ever had, and
OL,19,Factually were armed with nuclear
OL,20,Fweapons as a means to deliver their
OL,21,Fmessage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
