OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FFor these reasons, the United States
OL,8,Fmilitary is undertaking a massive and
OL,9,Fongoing operation to prevent this very
OL,10,Fwicked, radical dictatorship from
OL,11,Fthreatening America and our core
OL,12,Fnational security interests. We're
OL,13,Fgoing to destroy their missiles and
OL,14,Fraze their missile industry to the
OL,15,Fground. It will be totally again
OL,16,Fobliterated. We're going to annihilate
OL,17,Ftheir navy. We're going to ensure that
OL,18,Fthe region's terrorist proxies can no
OL,19,Flonger destabilize the region or the
OL,20,Fworld and attack our forces, and no
OL,21,Flonger use their IEDs, or roadside
OL,22,Fbombs as they are sometimes called, to
OL,23,Fso gravely wound and kill thousands
OL,24,Fand thousands of people, including
OL,25,Fmany Americans. And we will ensure
OL,26,Fthat Iran does not obtain a nuclear
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
