OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FThis regime will soon learn that no
OL,8,Fone should challenge the strength and
OL,9,Fmight of the United States Armed
OL,10,FForces. I built and rebuilt our
OL,11,Fmilitary in my first administration
OL,12,Fand there is no military on earth even
OL,13,Fclose to its power, strength or
OL,14,Fsophistication. My administration is
OL,15,Ftaking every possible step to minimize
OL,16,Fthe risk to U.S. personnel in the
OL,17,Fregion. Even so, and I do not make
OL,18,Fthis statement lightly, the Iranian
OL,19,Fregime seeks to kill. The lives of
OL,20,Fcourageous American heroes may be
OL,21,Flost, and we may have casualties. That
OL,22,Foften happens in war. But we're doing
OL,23,Fthis not for now. We're doing this for
OL,24,Fthe future. And it is a noble mission.
OL,25,FWe pray for every service member as
OL,26,Fthey selflessly risk their lives to
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
