OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FTo the members of the Islamic
OL,8,FRevolutionary Guard, the armed forces
OL,9,Fand all of the police, I say tonight
OL,10,Fthat you must lay down your weapons
OL,11,Fand have complete immunity. Or in the
OL,12,Falternative, face certain death. So,
OL,13,Flay down your arms. You will be
OL,14,Ftreated fairly with total immunity, or
OL,15,Fyou will face certain death. Finally,
OL,16,Fto the great proud people of Iran, I
OL,17,Fsay tonight that the hour of your
OL,18,Ffreedom is at hand. Stay sheltered.
OL,19,FDon't leave your home. It's very
OL,20,Fdangerous outside. Bombs will be
OL,21,Fdropping everywhere. When we are
OL,22,Ffinished, take over your government.
OL,23,FIt will be yours to take. This will be
OL,24,Fprobably your only chance for
OL,25,Fgenerations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
