OL,3,C'Massive and ongoing operation':
OL,4,CPresident Trump's statement on Iran in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FFor many years, you have asked for
OL,8,FAmerica's help. But you never got it.
OL,9,FNo president was willing to do what I
OL,10,Fam willing to do tonight. Now you have
OL,11,Fa president who is giving you what you
OL,12,Fwant. So let's see how you respond.
OL,13,FAmerica is backing you with
OL,14,Foverwhelming strength and devastating
OL,15,Fforce. Now is the time to seize
OL,16,Fcontrol of your destiny, and to
OL,17,Funleash the prosperous and glorious
OL,18,Ffuture that is close within your
OL,19,Freach. This is the moment for action.
OL,20,FDo not let it pass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
